Cisco-IOS-XR-asic-errors-oper API API Reference

API generated from Cisco-IOS-XR-asic-errors-oper@2017-09-07.yang

API Endpoint
http://{Controller-IP}:{Controller-Port}/restconf/operational/network-topology:network-topology/topology/topology-netconf/node/{{router}}/yang-ext:mount/
URL '/' code: %2F
Schemes: http
Version: 1.0.0

Paths

ASIC-ERRORS - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-asic-errors-oper:asic-errors/

Retrieve operation of resource: asic-errors

200 OK
asic-errors_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

NODES - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-asic-errors-oper:asic-errors/nodes/

Retrieve operation of resource: nodes

200 OK
nodes_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

NODE - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-asic-errors-oper:asic-errors/nodes/node/{node-name}/

Retrieve operation of resource: node

node-name: string
in path

ID of node-name

200 OK
node_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

          },
          
"asic": "string" Asic string

        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

ASIC-INFORMATION - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-asic-errors-oper:asic-errors/nodes/node/{node-name}/asic-information/{asic}/

Retrieve operation of resource: asic-information

node-name: string
in path

ID of node-name

asic: string
in path

ID of asic

200 OK
asic-information_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json

INSTANCE - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-asic-errors-oper:asic-errors/nodes/node/{node-name}/asic-information/{asic}/instances/instance/{asic-instance}/

Retrieve operation of resource: instance

node-name: string
in path

ID of node-name

asic: string
in path

ID of asic

asic-instance: string
in path

ID of asic-instance

200 OK
instance_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK)

ERROR-PATH - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-asic-errors-oper:asic-errors/nodes/node/{node-name}/asic-information/{asic}/instances/instance/{asic-instance}/error-path/

Retrieve operation of resource: error-path

node-name: string
in path

ID of node-name

asic: string
in path

ID of asic

asic-instance: string
in path

ID of asic-instance

200 OK
error-path_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK)
